title: Alzheimer 's in the U.S : lifetime risks , by age and gender
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 2 different Countrys on X-axis for 2 groups Men, and Women. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
In Country 65 years, Women had the highest SOME LABEL 211.0 among the 2 groups and in 45 years, Men had the lowest SOME LABEL 103.0.
Among all the Countrys, Women had the highest SOME LABEL 211.0 in Country 65 years and lowest value 116.0 in Country 45 years.
Country 65 years and 45 years had the biggest gap of 95.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for Women.
min_summary: This grouped bar chart represents 2 different Countrys on X-axis for 2 groups Men, and Women. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
